summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2334, for the improvement of East John Street, from Bellevue Avenue North to Summit Avenue North; all in the City of Seattle, by grading the same; under Ordinance No. 24160 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
